		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I get NES related drams once in awhile but definitely not regularly. It's also not possible to remember the most part of them unfortunately.
<br />
<br />The best I had was about me playing some game (I think the game in question doesn't even exist, it was somewhere between Castlevania and Battletoads) and I discovered a secret alternate path that almost doubled the size of the game, and I remember the alternate path was very hard and very intense, and I guess included a racing level or something in the like (think something like Battletoads).
<br />
<br />But that's about everything. Of course this is never going to happen, because how memory is expensive in NES games, nobody would hide half of it's levels in a hard to find secret.

		

